            "creation_date": 1466955604,
            "body": "<p>I tried the github version of your application, added a test and it worked fine: <a href=\"https://github.com/michalmela/hestalis\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://github.com/michalmela/hestalis<\/a> .<\/p>\n\n<p>Check your test configuration. Also, please don't follow the advice from the other response to add interfaces for services for no good reason.<\/p>\n",
